{"tid":945281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有感而發 呢一代嘅年青人簡直不撚柒知所謂","createTime":"2018-12-17T17:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T18:06:23.000Z","uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28d0c2148684b7370e73bba2e6b114a3703d4f43","tid":945281,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"未識串嘴就要串 仲要講串唔起 串到一撚定要人覺得佢好威<br />\n塊面永遠向地 條腰永遠唔直 手永遠喺度串來串去一係就嘴苖苖<br />\n成日自己好撚勁覺撚得人哋係一定係白痴但又唔記得自己只係毒/戅鳩個口來來去去都係咁口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n串完人哋之後就要講要求講態度講權利等等十幾歲就學人講投拆老師<br />\n好嘞 自己有小小聰明掉撚返轉個角色扮自己係神<br />\n佢就識話啲老師要求過高無理取鬧就學人嚴三嚴四<br />\n含撚啦真係<br />\n個情況就係咁loop.............................................. <br />\n打呢篇嘢唔係諗撚著你會改<br />\n只係想屌你老尾 明未?!"},{"pid":"1aebb1170aaa3bac37f953b74e6583afce6dcf33","tid":945281,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"628f0ed3fd2fdfb015ac3462c1b697a35b1b7baf","tid":945281,"uid":216030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"謝教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7223144866a9a0bdc2dc88d2d81e86d8e129caa7","tid":945281,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1aebb1170aaa3bac37f953b74e6583afce6dcf33","tid":945281,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"真你又夫皮"},{"pid":"8bc423203dd65e02a7ac18c8018d4838205228f2","tid":945281,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"628f0ed3fd2fdfb015ac3462c1b697a35b1b7baf","tid":945281,"uid":216030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"謝教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"改漏個嫌字添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12706505